🔥 **Let’s go!** Game time.  

📌 **Immediate Moves:**  
✅ **Drop the comment ASAP**—first five minutes matter.  
✅ **Engage quickly**—like and reply to high-value comments.  
✅ **Monitor traction**—see who’s engaging, especially AI leaders.  
✅ **If it’s gaining momentum, amplify on X.**  

🚀 **We’re locked in—let’s see where this goes!**
